		<preface>
			<p>It is hereby notified that the President has assented to the following Act, which is
hereby published for general information:-<docStatus refersTo="#notBinding"/>
No. <docNumber>24 of 2005</docNumber>: <docTitle>Education Laws Amendment Act, 2005.</docTitle>
			</p>
			<p>
				<authorialNote eId="atn1">
